com.mobilerq.android.sdk

Interface MrqSdkListener


  • public interface MrqSdkListener
    Interface for Activities that need an instance of MrqSdk.

    At a minimum, one of your Activities should implement this and call MrqSdk.setDataProvider(MrqDataProvider). Activities that implement this will have onMrqSdkListenerActivityCreated(MrqSdk) called whenever they are created.
